## Limitations

The findings presented in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on gender communication differences. The data is limited to the sources accessed, and there may be newer studies or alternative viewpoints not covered. Additionally, societal and cultural factors influencing communication styles are complex and may not be fully captured in this report.